snippet.title: The War Within - Highlights
snippet.description:
The War Within is live on PC! 
Log in now and download the update for new Gameplay, Enemies, Weapons, Customizations, a new Mission Type, dozens of story secrets, and more!

For more info visit http://www.warframe.com.
